Important modern practices

· Use the -ktx extensions (e.g., firebase-firestore-ktx) – they bring Kotlin coroutine and Flow support, plus more idiomatic APIs.
· Firebase BoM – always declare the BoM and omit explicit versions on individual Firebase libraries.
· SafetyNet deprecation – Phone Auth now uses Play Integrity API by default; make sure to follow the migration guide if you use phone sign-in.

