2. Alternatives to Firebase (quick comparison)

Platform Database Open Source? Self-host option? Best for…
Supabase PostgreSQL Yes Yes (or cloud) SQL lovers, real-time, RLS
Appwrite MariaDB / custom Yes Yes Simpler API, file storage, functions
Backendless Proprietary No Cloud only Low-code, visual builder
AWS Amplify DynamoDB / RDS Partly No (AWS managed) Large-scale, AWS ecosystem
Parse Platform MongoDB / PostgreSQL Yes Yes Self-hosted, legacy Parse API

Migration pain points: Firestore → SQL is hard; Auth migration requires password resets or custom tokens. If you’re considering switching, evaluate early.

